								"jobs",
								"SIDetection"
							]
						},
						"description": "Create a synchronous SI Detection job. Waits for the detection to complete before returning the result.\n\nThe `jobId`, `fdfFileId`, `fdfDekToken`, and `redactions` are automatically saved from the response."
					},
